title: Ep - 24 - Lindsay Hubbard and Everett Weston from Summer House
description:
Lindsay Hubbard and Everett Weston from Summer House discuss their romance and sharing a house in the Hamptons, Emily and Jessica from Housewives Kiki show review TLC’s new show Brother Husbands, and Ben Schirmer explains how he and spouse watch Real Housewives of Beverly Hills and Vanderpump Rules religiously.
